    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>STEEL ALLIANCE CONFIRMED</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Samuel Len</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Len, Samuel</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Pohang Iron and Steel Co and Nippon Steel, world's two largest steelmakers, will purchase more shares in each other to minimize direct competition in Asian markets (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The world's two largest steel makers agreed to buy more shares in each other to minimize direct competition in Asian markets. The Pohang Iron and Steel Company and Nippon Steel are raising to 3 percent their intended purchases of each other's shares within 18 months, the two companies said in a joint statement.</p>
        <p>Samuel Len</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
